Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.92,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanna ski already!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're approaching Yashagatake now. \NWe'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a chilling name \N for a place like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimoto-sensei, did you know
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this was the site of an old battlefield \Nfrom the Sengoku era?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,An old battlefield?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it was named after the ghosts of soldiers
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.73,0:00:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who were burned alive in that castle and became wandering Yaksha. {demonic warriors}{?????? I don't understand shit in this line}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're not here\Nfor a test of courage.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a ski training camp.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hagiwara-san, that's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That concludes the room assignments.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, finally! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, everyone, \Ncarry your luggage to your rooms!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.57,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to skiing, \Nbut also this year's {\i1}ritual{\i0}. {???? think she says kotoshi no are mo - this year's "that thing" - will see}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.93,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're finally here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already drenched in sweat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, feels great!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So bold!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and this is even better!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.08,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Saori? \NNo one's watching.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.53,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I put on my bra and shorts.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. It feels amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Teach me too! {?? teach her what? to masturbate?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami-san, honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, just do whatever you want! {maybe "you can do it on your own/you don't need a teacher"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I-It's so cold!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.96,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No self-respecting man would go in \Nfor wimpy skiing with the girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.18,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the cold wind refine your spirit! \NThat is the tradition of Jouka! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NSaori and the others sure have it easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,There's a world of difference \Nbetween boys and girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear your mind, Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next! Begin the cold-wind endurance! {???? nc what's masatsu here, and we don't see them doing anything later to be sure, I assume they're just going to spar now}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,Man, this is unbearable!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.27,0:03:44.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! I wanna look too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Classic briefs. {pantsu}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, give it here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.33,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want more!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.44,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I said, stop! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A flag signal. {semaphore (hand) flag}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.11,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Es-cape is im-pos-sible."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Yuji-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's get into the bath \None more time and wait for him. {?? I hear "shower in one more bath"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go wash each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Lend me the soap.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your shampoo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.27,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes down to it, \N{\i1}we'll{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}have to do it, the three of us. {idk what this is about}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit lacking in impact, though. {presence}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the annual hazing \Nof the new teacher is upon us. {scaring}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And this year's target is Akimoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Half-hearted stuff won't work on her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.32,0:05:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can make that sexy teacher who\Ntoys with the boys cry uncle, it'll be a huge hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun promised to help, though. {[yet he's still not here]}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.02,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even better, if a real ghost showed up, \Nit'd really liven things up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, don't say weird stuff like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Squish, squish...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sakazaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup! Did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when there's a worthy goal, \Nnothing is impossible for me. {lit: when [I/you] feel like it}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're impossible! {??? easily mixed up (e.g. similar words); easily mistaken; confusing; misleading; equivocal; ambiguous - idk what she means, perhaps that he was supposed to scare akimoto, not her}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! That hurts! \NDon't you know I've got frostbite?! {yep}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.54,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's back already.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh. I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, listen... and then... \NSo you do this... and that...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.42,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear some strange voices \Nfrom deep inside the building just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the rumors, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.28,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That this lodge was built \Non the site of a razed fortress.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... know.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.74,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're too nosy, \Nyou might even summon some old spirits. {lit: dig too deep}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, teacher,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.85,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to ask \Nfor your advice on something. {??? atashi ***tte go soudan}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I could advise you \Njust fine in the lobby. {corridor}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the others might hear us there!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop that! You're on a\Nschool trip, and th-that's improper...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.55,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk to you \Nabout something, that's all!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really as childish as they say? {meaning "underdeveloped [body]"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have no feminine charm at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No... you're very charming. \NMore than enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cappy! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone always makes fun of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And it kept bothering me... so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.06,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, now h-hurry up \Nand put your clothes on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.69,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! {I saw it!}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, teacher, how naughty! {/that won't do}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.98,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You just said you'd raise \Nmy makeup test score a little if I do this. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's favoritism if I ever saw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, give me that photo!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.11,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come and take it, Fukuike-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.38,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, while we're at it, \Nmaybe I should ask for a favor too?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you special service, teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.69,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! Here, water.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff sure is strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All done here. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,Must be my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... this one!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.82,0:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This blizzard will be over by morning, it seems.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls should go to bed soon too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought your dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. {for your trouble}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.14,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how is Fukuike-sensei? \NJust a cold, I hope?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.73,0:09:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, apparently he suddenly \Ndeveloped a fever of unknown cause. {chills}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He took some medicine and turned in early.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the curse of the spirits?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits? {onryo - vengeful ghosts}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.06,0:09:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.57,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,On stormy nights like this, \Nthe restless spirits go wandering around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've heard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous. \NThat's just superstition.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.74,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But Fukuike-sensei was drenched in sweat, \Nlike he was being haunted by something. {possessed}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.49,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard this lodge was built \Non the ruins of Yashagatake Fortress.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but I feel…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.30,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, strange incidents of an\Nunknown nature occur here from time to time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.23,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an open secret among the graduates.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.31,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Then that mysterious case \Nof the suicide jumper too...? {probably an incident of someone jumping to their death}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.10,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Aside from the academy's higher-ups, \Nonly a few people know. {??? gakuin no *** ijo; maybe "to save face of the academy, ..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.96,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you see it can't be explained \Nby anything else but the curse? {it's strange if it has nothing to do with a curse}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even last year, in the bathtub...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That razor suicide, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.12,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't that the room \N Akimoto-sensei is staying in this year?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.74,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's just a coincidence. \NYes, obviously just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.73,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough for tonight. \NWe have an early morning tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.61,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we should definitely sleep together tonight, the three of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you, I'm scared too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.17,0:11:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Fukuike-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really that sick?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.48,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! It's cold. \NI should've left the heater on.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird... Maybe it's because of this blizzard?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What am I even scared of?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's just old ghost stories for students.} It's just some kids' ghost stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm just hearing things...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, I'm seeing things too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only freaking out \Nbecause I tend to overthink things.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to warm up and calm myself down.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all times to be alone...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course, it can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.90,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.76,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The door won't open! \NSomeone help me, anyone! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay! {yurusen?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all pay for it! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.73,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the lord of this fortress.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.25,0:14:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has a shameless young woman \Nsuch as you come to this place? {???? some obsolete talk, can't make shit out}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wicked deeds are plain to see! {crimes}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissatisfied with toying with countless men,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.66,0:15:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you dare, while holding\Nthe sacred post of teacher,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.49,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to seduce innocent young lambs as well?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I would never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.87,0:15:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Even now you still feign ignorance?! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.48,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I understand! \NI swear I'll never do such things again!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Never shall you dare think of it! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.96,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we go a bit too far this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.56,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sakazaki-kun?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was all something you set up? {omae?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all. In fact, \NI'm just a special guest today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls…\NJust what is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.60,0:15:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! This is actually \Nour annual “new teacher scare” ritual. {"hazing" previously}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.06,0:15:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This year, it fell to us to carry it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.73,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Then the door not opening \Nwas your doing too?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, not bad, Akimoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only female teacher \Nso far who didn't faint.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on passing it! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.89,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a joke, see? This is where you\Nlaugh it off and forgive us. Right, teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Saori?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't tell me she's still on the balcony!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Someone!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Saori, are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.33,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't in the script... {/part of the plan}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori! Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.53,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori! Where are you?! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.36,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is Saori's costume!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.09,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,an old escape tunnel from the fortress?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,From back then…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bargain-bin playboy Hoi Hideki!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You really hurt my\Npride back then, y'know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I treated you to some real \NAmerican-style special effects makeup.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hold it! Are you for real?! {???? joudan?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That look suits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! {waka - young master}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Give that back!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.59,0:19:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't let go of the controls!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My bra!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Keep her steady! {all right}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! They're the mummies I've discovered.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put them on display in our hotel lobby!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this prank going a little too far?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to use plenty of adhesive. {?? to wrap them in cloth ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves them right for that amateur makeup stunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!{Marty: There is an untranslated line here from Saori}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.23,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Well said! {probably? no idea}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've finally found you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.89,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop right there! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{marching chant}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.39,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No slacking off! The heptathlon's\Nnext after the snowfield running! {idk what else this nanashu could be}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Principal! Don't move! {???????}{also idk why he calls him kyoto - vice principal now if he was chairman before}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal! {/sorry}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Get him now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Stop! Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.76,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't! Please forgive us! {???}
Comment: 10,0:21:01.64,0:21:01.69,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 4,0:21:01.69,0:21:06.57,Song,,0,0,0,,{BECAUSE by ScooP; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: 見ようともしなかったことに\N君は今瞳を向け始めてる\N「ゴメンネ」とうつむいた君\N僕にはもう信じさせるものがない\N崩れそうなその肩を二度と\N僕は抱けない\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 離れて行く\N怖いなんて言葉にはつばを吐いてきた\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 小さくなる\Nあの頃は君の好きなもの すべて好きだったのに\N手に届く限りのもので\N君は今 幸せを創りあげたね\N夢を側に置きたい君\N夢だけはまだ追い続けていたい僕\N君はたぶん僕以外の男に\N抱かれるんだね\N君が思ってるより 僕は強くないさ\N誰も君の代わりできないから\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 振り向かない\N君の笑顔 今僕の瞳駆けめぐる\NBecause I miss you, Baby. もう見えない\N届かない僕の愛も夢もこの声さえも\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\N小さくなる\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\Nもう見えない} You're starting to turn your eyes
Dialogue: 4,0:21:07.70,0:21:15.71,Song,,0,0,0,,to something you never even tried to see
Dialogue: 4,0:21:17.08,0:21:22.06,Song,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry," you said, bowing your head
Dialogue: 4,0:21:22.80,0:21:31.71,Song,,0,0,0,,And I no longer had anything you could believe in
Dialogue: 4,0:21:32.68,0:21:38.45,Song,,0,0,0,,I can never hold
Dialogue: 4,0:21:39.13,0:21:46.83,Song,,0,0,0,,those shaking shoulders again {crumbling}
Dialogue: 4,0:21:46.83,0:21:50.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:50.58,0:21:53.96,Song,,0,0,0,,I won't look back
Dialogue: 4,0:21:53.96,0:22:02.06,Song,,0,0,0,,Your smile is flashing through my eyes now
Dialogue: 4,0:22:02.06,0:22:05.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:05.60,0:22:09.27,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 4,0:22:09.27,0:22:20.99,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, my dreams, and even my voice won't reach you
Dialogue: 4,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.99,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H880049&}Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby {sounds like an audio drop after this line, but most people skip the ending song so eh}
Dialogue: 4,0:22:28.79,0:22:32.00,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm getting smaller
Dialogue: 4,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:40.01,0:22:44.01,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:44.01,0:22:48.01,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 4,0:22:48.01,0:22:52.02,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:55.61,0:22:59.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby...
